4. **Teleport Handling**: When a state (i, j, t) is processed, if it improves minCostForValue_level[t] for its cell value, suffix_min_level[t] is updated. Then, for all cells (x, y), if t < k, the minimal cost to teleport to (x, y) (using suffix_min_level[t]) is used to update dp[x][y][t+1].

